\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  And the Lord God saw the earth, and it was corrupted; because all flesh had corrupted its way upon the earth. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 14.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 
