\f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 2.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  For she is on lofty eminences, and stands in the midst of the ways. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 
3.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  For she sits by the gates of princes, and sings in the entrances, saying, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 4.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 
\ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  You, O men, I exhort; and utter my voice to the sons of men. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 5.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  O ye simple, understand subtlety, and ye that are untaught, imbibe knowledge. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 6.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  Hearken to me; for I will speak solemn truths; and will produce right sayings from my lips. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 7.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  For my throat shall meditate truth; and false lips are an abomination before me. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 8.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  All the words of my mouth are in righteousness; there is nothing in them wrong or perverse. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 9.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  They are all evident to those that understand, and right to those that find knowledge. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 10.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  Receive instruction, and not silver; and knowledge rather than tried gold. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 11.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  For wisdom is better than precious stones; and no valuable substance is of equal worth with it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 12.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  I wisdom have dwelt with counsel and knowledge, and I have called upon understanding. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 13.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  The fear of the Lord hates unrighteousness, and insolence, and pride, and the ways of wicked men; and I hate the perverse ways of bad men. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 
14.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  Counsel and safety are mine: prudence is mine, and strength is mine. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 15.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  By me kings reign, and princes decree justice. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 16.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 
 By me nobles become great, and monarchs by me rule over the earth. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 17.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 
 I love those that love me; and they that seek me shall find me. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \f230\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871 18.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f230\fs32\insrsid7547747\charrsid8406871  Wealth and glory 
