 A wise son makes his father glad: but a foolish son is a grief to his mother. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 2.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 Treasures shall not profit the lawless: but righteousness shall deliver from death. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 3.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 The Lord will not famish a righteous soul: but he will overthrow the life of the ungodly. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 4.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 Poverty brings a man low: but the hands of the vigorous make rich. A son who is instructed shall be wise, and shall use the fool for a servant. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 5.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 A wise son is saved from heat: but a lawless son is blighted of the winds in harvest. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 6.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 The blessing of the Lord is upon the head of the just: but untimely grief shall cover the mouth of the ungodly. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 7.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 The memory of the just is praised; but the name of the ungodly man is extinguished. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 8.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 A wise man in heart will receive commandments; but he that is unguarded in his lips shall be overthrown in his perverseness. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 9.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 He that walks simply, walks confidently; but he that perverts his ways shall be known. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 10.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 He that winks with his eyes deceitfully, procures griefs for men; but he that reproves boldly is a peacemaker. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 11.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 There is a fountain of life in the hand of a righteous man; but destruction shall cover the mouth of the ungodly. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 12.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 Hatred stirs up strife; but affection covers all that do not love strife. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 13.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 He that brings forth wisdom from his lips smites the fool with a rod. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 14.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747  The wise will hide discretion; but the mouth of the hasty
 draws near to ruin. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 15.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747  The wealth of rich men is a strong city; but poverty is the ruin of the ungodly. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7547747 16.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747  The works of the righteous produce life; but the fruits of the ungodly produce sins. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 17.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747  Instruction keeps the right ways of life; but instruction unchastened goes astray. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 18.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 Righteous lips cover enmity; but they that utter railings are most foolish. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 19.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747 
 By a multitude of words thou shalt not escape sin; but if thou refrain thy lips thou wilt be prudent. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 20.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747  The tongue of the just is tried silver; 
but the heart of the ungodly shall fail. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 21.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747  The lips of the righteous know sublime truths: but the foolish die in want. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7547747 22.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 \cs35\f1\fs32\insrsid7547747  The blessing of the Lord is upon the head of the righteous; it enriches him, and grief of heart shall not be added to it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af2 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid7547747 
